name: Salyut 2
notes: Also referred to as "Kosmos 557", by Soviets to deny failure of another Salyut

name: Salyut 3
notes: First station to maintain orientation relative to Earth

name: Salyut 6
notes: First station with two docking ports, allowing resupply from Earth

name: International Space Station
notes: Largest ever modular space station, longest lived
